		<RichText x="66" y="1224" width="442" height="135" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">战斗装甲：每个装甲吸附所需7s，总蓄力时长<span color="#ffdfbf">7/12/17s</span><span>，可被超载破坏；海捷德吸附后持续2个技能或至多18s卸下。<br/>被阻挡后掉落地面，为附近2m内角色提供加成：攻击力提升</span><span color="#ffdfbf">40%</span><span>，持续8s，可叠加，每层单独计算。<br/>冻结：冻结一次</span><span color="#ffccbf">+12*D</span><span>，满计量</span><span color="#ffccbf">36</span><span>，冻结后吸附装甲造成真伤后解除；D为影响因子，会受到多人模式影响(D=1/0.9/0.83/0.8)，</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/海捷德.assets/Image_16.png')" x="66" y="71" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
