		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="255" width="433" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">海捷德不紧不慢地打两个近拳，均造成<span color="#ffebbf">40%</span><span>伤害。装备装甲后伤害翻倍，当装备1/2/3个装甲时，就会进行1/2/4次连续普攻。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="409" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">处于后方时，海捷德用力打出下勾拳，造成<span color="#ffebbf">40%</span><span>伤害。装备装甲后伤害翻倍。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="767" width="441" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">海捷德立即蓄力，随后冲向玩家造成<span color="#ffebbf">60%,15%</span><span>伤害。装备装甲后，冲刺造成</span><span color="#ffebbf">100%,25%</span><span>伤害，当装备1/2/3个装甲时，就会进行2/4/8次冲刺，且冲刺距离大幅加长。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1023" width="442" height="316" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">一段时间后，或者海捷德生命值低于<span color="#ffdfbf">80%/60%/40%</span><span>时，海捷德会在战斗中尝试吸附「</span><span textDecoration="underline">战斗装甲</span><span>」强化战斗，第</span><span color="#ffdfbf">1/2/<br/>&gt;2</span><span>次蓄力将召唤</span><span color="#ffdfbf">1/2/3</span><span>个装甲；若处于深境螺旋则直接召唤</span><span color="#ffdfbf">3</span><span>个装甲。<br/>对海捷德持续触发</span><span color="#99ffff">冻结反应</span><span>可冻结她，使其无法装备装甲，每个装甲在吸收时将对其造成</span><span color="#ffdfbf">5%生命值</span><span>的真伤；<br/>对装甲触发</span><span color="#ff66aa">超载反应</span><span>可直接炸毁；<br/>或者</span><span color="#ffff99">阻挡路径</span><span>同样可以阻止吸附，使其掉落为角色提供增益。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
